node.text: "But if we learned anything from sports, is that no matter how far down we may be, we are never too far down to come back."
The Houston-based rapper brings his workwear touch to Nike SB, adding bandana patterns, rope-style fat laces, and more to the fat-tongued gem.

node.title: Unboxing Travis Scott's Nike SB Dunk collaboration

node.text: This upcoming All-Star Weekend in Chicago is sure to be packed with must-have releases. Check out this quick recap of what Jordan, Nike, and Converse have prepared for mid-February.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Sneaker News on September 11, 2021. May be an image of 4 people, footwear and text.

node.text: Tag *that* person in your friend group who does this

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Sneaker News on September 11, 2021. May be an image of footwear.

node.text: A clean mix of green shades appear on this upcoming Air Force 1 LX "Toasty", with just a touch of blue on the quilted panel at the mid-foot. Expect these at Nike retailers very soon! Hit the link in our bio for a closer look.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Sneaker News on September 10, 2021. May be an image of footwear and outdoors.

node.text: This is cool: On every pair in the @natgeo x Reebok collection, a unique QR code on the tongue that provides exclusive access to 360 immersive videos of the environment that inspired the product. Tap the link in our bio to see the full capsule.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Sneaker News on September 10, 2021. May be an image of footwear and text that says 'SEP 21 $160 NIKE KD 14 "RON ENGLISH 1"'.

node.text: #SNReleaseAlert : The Nike KD 14 "Ron English 1" is scheduled to release on September 21st for $160. The LA-based artist has helped KD broaden his scope of art, and this friendship comes full circle with this collaborative release. Hit the link in our bio for more details.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Sneaker News on September 10, 2021. May be an image of footwear.

node.text: A third colorway of the Nike SB Blazer Mid Acclimate appears; inspired by hiking, this upcoming release sees classic Oregon colors that touch on the PNW's love of the great outdoors. These are expected in November; hit the link in our bio to see more.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Sneaker News on September 10, 2021. May be an image of footwear.

node.text: Nike bridges old and new once again with the Fontanka Waffle. Taking the Waffle Trainer upper, Nike applies a blocky midsole that features a thick React sole at the heel. Tap the link in our bio to get a closer look.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Sneaker News on September 10, 2021. May be an image of footwear.

node.text: Halloween...already? adidas is preparing the Superstar in a spooky manner fit for the end-of-October holiday. Hit the link in our bio to see a closer look; these are dropping soon.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Sneaker News on September 10, 2021. May be an image of footwear and text.

node.text: #SNReleaseAlert : The Gundam Unicorn x Nike SB Dunk High is officially releasing on SNKRS on September 27th, 2021 for $110. Hit the link in our bio to see full official images.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Sneaker News on September 10, 2021. May be an image of footwear.

node.text: Halloween Huaraches? Nike is preparing this iconic 1991 runner in a color scheme befitting the spooky holiday. Tap the link in our bio for a first look.
